          style="width: 100%">

                   width="55" />

                   label="Object1" />

                   label="Attribute1"
                   :min-width="minWidth" />
  <el-table-column prop="msgt"
                   :min-width="minWidth"
                   label="Type" />
  <el-table-column prop="cobj"
                   :min-width="minWidth"
                   label="Object2" />
  <el-table-column prop="catt"
                   :min-width="minWidth"
                   label="Attribute2" />
  <el-table-column prop="acat"
                   :min-width="minWidth"
                   label="Category" />

                   :min-width="minWidth"
                   label="Subroutine" />
